Back in 2012, the animal welfare group Mercy For Animals released a video that purported to show shocking animal cruelty at a farm in Hansen, Idaho. The farm, Bettencourt Dairies' Dry Creek Dairy, was a supplier of dairy products to Burger King, and the hidden camera video showed workers kicking, punching, and jumping on top of cows.
